➜【星连文学社】苏坛：《老地标》
http://www.sohu.com/a/415203640_100115135	39413
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7cef697e4dfb4959b1bbc978544ca6a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《老地标》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">市井、巷口和弄堂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进出的是平淡的生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">讲述的也只是张长李短</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>马头墙依旧耸立</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>矢巷早已不卖弓箭盾牌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>毛家场还有姓毛的人家</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">校园里的文庙荡然无存</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过读书声从未中断</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西禅寺已经没有了钟声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>繁华的街市和高楼下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有着长久不变的人情冷暖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>老地标挂在斑驳的墙上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/064b10489bf2424da1edda4c7413fa68.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
